<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmạ lqytny wạqf mkạny bạỷs kdh rạḍy bḥạly
 zy mflwj msẖ qạdr yqwm mn ktr ạlhmwm ʿạysẖ mhzwm
 (ṭlbt kẖlạṣh wạ̉kyd ạ̹kẖlạṣh hymd ạ̹ydyh wyḥn ʿlyạ
 dạ ạ̉nạ ạ̉yh mn gẖyrh mạswạsẖ mn gẖyrh gẖyr ạ̹nsạn kẖạṭy mlyạn bkẖṭyh)2
 ạlqrạr - wlmạ qblth gẖyrly ḥyạty lmsny bqwh bdl kẖṭwạty
 rfʿny lyh gẖsl rjlyạ msḥ ly dmwʿy wḍmny lyh
 (sẖạl ḥml ktạfy yswʿ ạlsẖạfy wḥḍnh ạldạfy mlạny kẖlạṣ
 ạ̹dạny trnymh wḥn ʿlyạ whbny ạlnṣrh lmsny yswʿ)2
 2- ḍmny kẖlyny ạ̉ʿysẖlk wạtrmy fy bḥwr ḥnạnk
 rdny ạsyb ạlʿạlm wạ̉nḥny qdạm rjlyk
 (tʿbạn wạlkẖṭwh ạljạyh bʿydh wṣʿbh bqạlhạ zmạn
 ḥyrạn msẖ lạqy ḥyạty fy sẖr fy dnyạ mạ lyhạ ạ̉mạn)2</lyrics>
